---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About Rentar — Fuel Catalyst Technology | Rentar"
  description="Rentar Environmental Solutions: two decades of fuel catalyst innovation. 33 international patents, deployed across 20+ countries, with over one million compatible engine configurations."
>
  <section class="hero" style="min-height:45vh;">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-tag">The Company</p>
      <h1 style="font-size:2.6rem;">The Rentar story</h1>
      <p>Two decades of fuel catalyst innovation. 33 international patents. Deployed across 20+ countries. One simple idea: better combustion means less fuel.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <p class="section-label">Our Story</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Built on a simple idea: better combustion means less fuel</h2>
      <div class="manifesto-block">
        <p>Rentar Environmental Solutions has spent over two decades developing, testing, and deploying fuel catalyst technology in the world's most demanding industrial environments. From open-pit mines in Brazil to offshore platforms in the Atlantic, from agricultural fleets across the Midwest to marine vessels transiting global shipping lanes, Rentar technology is proven where fuel consumption matters most.</p>
        <p class="manifesto-highlight">33 international patents. No moving parts. No electronics. No maintenance. Just measurable results.</p>
        <p>The company was founded on a deceptively simple premise: if you can improve the combustion efficiency of diesel fuel at the molecular level before it reaches the engine, you can reduce fuel consumption, lower emissions, and extend engine life, all without modifying the engine itself.</p>
        <p>That premise became the Rentar Fuel Catalyst, a passive in-line device that installs in the fuel line upstream of the engine. It conditions fuel to burn more completely, extracting more energy from every drop. No moving parts. No electronics. No ongoing maintenance. Just physics.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-light">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">By the Numbers</p>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="text-align:center;">Rentar at a glance</h2>
      <div class="stats-grid" style="max-width:900px; margin:48px auto;">
        <div style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="stat-number" style="color:var(--navy);">33</div>
          <div class="stat-label" style="color:var(--gray-text);">international<br>patents</div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="stat-number" style="color:var(--navy);">20+</div>
          <div class="stat-label" style="color:var(--gray-text);">countries<br>deployed</div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="stat-number" style="color:var(--navy);">1M+</div>
          <div class="stat-label" style="color:var(--gray-text);">engines<br>compatible</div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="stat-number" style="color:var(--navy);">2003</div>
          <div class="stat-label" style="color:var(--gray-text);">year Rentar<br>was founded</div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="stat-number" style="color:var(--navy);">0</div>
          <div class="stat-label" style="color:var(--gray-text);">moving parts<br>in the catalyst</div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="stat-number" style="color:var(--navy);">10%</div>
          <div class="stat-label" style="color:var(--gray-text);">average fuel<br>efficiency gain</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <p class="section-label">Mission</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Reduce global fuel consumption. Measure the impact.</h2>
      <div class="manifesto-block">
        <p>Every gallon of diesel not burned is a gallon that doesn't produce CO2. Rentar's mission is to deploy fuel catalyst technology at scale across the world's highest-fuel-consuming industries, delivering measurable fuel savings, verified emissions reductions, and operational intelligence to asset operators worldwide.</p>
        <p>We believe that meaningful emissions reduction starts with better combustion. Our technology, combined with telemetry and analytics through the GHGsolve Intelligence Platform, gives operators the data to prove it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background:var(--navy); text-align:center;">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <p class="section-label" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">Get in touch</p>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="color:var(--white);">Learn more about Rentar</h2>
      <p class="section-text" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7); margin-bottom:40px;">Contact our team to learn about the technology, explore validation data, or discuss a proof-of-concept deployment for your operations.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact us</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
